OL,7,FAslef union announced five of its
OL,8,Fmembers - Chiltern, c2c, East
OL,9,FMidlands, Northern and TransPennine -
OL,10,Fvoted to carry on strike action
OL,12,Fat five rail operators have voted to
OL,13,Fcontinue taking strike action for six
OL,14,Fmonths in the long-running dispute
OL,15,Fover pay and conditions.
OL,17,FAslef announced that its members on
OL,18,FChiltern, c2c, East Midlands, Northern
OL,19,Fand TransPennine railways had
OL,20,Foverwhelmingly backed carrying on with
OL,21,Faction.
