OL,7,F"We want to find a resolution to this
OL,8,Fdispute, for members who have not had
OL,9,Fa pay rise since our last deals ran
OL,10,Fout in 2019, and the only way to
OL,11,Fresolve this dispute is for the
OL,12,Femployers, and the government that
OL,13,Fstands behind them, to come and talk
OL,14,Fto us."
